X-WR-CALNAME:Mildmay line disruption
BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-07-01T03:30:00&endDate=2026-07-01T05:15:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nMILDMAY LINE: Tuesday 30 June\, Wednesday 1\, Thursday 2 and Friday 3 July\, until 0615\, no southbound service from Willesden Junction to Shepherds Bush. The 0611 train from Stratford to Clapham Junction starts from Shepherds Bush and the 0651 from Stratford to Richmond will start from Acton Central. The 0552 first train from Willesden Junction to Clapham Junction starts from Shepherds Bush at 0600 and the 0608 second train from Willesden Junction to Clapham Junction does not run. Use the next service at 0623 or local bus routes 220 or 228.
DTEND:20260701T051500Z
DTSTART:20260701T033000Z
SUMMARY:Mildmay line: Part Closure
UID:a0d965f6-f95e-4ffe-8243-e1e6e5abaec6@a0d9.org
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-07-01T21:00:00&endDate=2026-07-01T22:30:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nMILDMAY LINE: Monday 29\, Tuesday 30 June\, Wednesday 1 and Thursday 2 July\, the 2203 and 2234 trains from Clapham Junction terminate at Willesden Junction instead of Stratford.
DTEND:20260701T223000Z
DTSTART:20260701T210000Z
SUMMARY:Mildmay line: Reduced Service
UID:09eedca7-0b61-4278-b2d9-0c26ee1337fb@09ee.org
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-07-02T22:45:00&endDate=2026-07-03T00:29:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nMILDMAY LINE: Monday 29\, Tuesday 30 June\, Wednesday 1 and Thursday 2 July\, after 2345 each evening\, no westbound service from Camden Road to Willesden Junction. The 2359 and 0015 services from Stratford will terminate at Camden Road. Use London Overground services from Euston to Willesden Junction\, Northern line from Camden Town\, or local bus routes 1\, 24\, 46 88 and 214 from Camden Road / Camden Town.
DTEND:20260703T002900Z
DTSTART:20260702T224500Z
SUMMARY:Mildmay line: Part Closure
